{
  "title": "ISic003473. Funerary monument of (?)Simylos",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag, April 2006</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σιμύλου\n                    Καλλιππίδα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σιμύλου\">[Σι?]μύλου̣</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Καλλιππίδα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Καλλιππίδα\">[Κ]α̣λλι̣ππίδα̣</span></span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag, April 2006</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σιμύλου\n                    Καλλιππίδα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σιμύλου\">[..]ΜΥΛΟ.</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Καλλιππίδα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Καλλιππίδα\">[.].ΛΛ.ΠΠΙΔ.</span></span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003473_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473_left_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_left_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473_left.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_left-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473_right_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_right_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473_right.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_right-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473_top_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_top_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003473_top.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2018-07-05\" src=\"ISic003473_top-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Manganaro: [Σ?]ι.ύλου</span></span><br></li><li><span class=\"2\">2: <span>Manganaro: [Κ]αλλιπίδα</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>(tomb) of Simylos son of Kallipidas</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The name Simylos is attested at Tauromenion and Akrai in the Hellenistic period, making it the most likely restoration of the name in line 1 (although one might note that both Κωμύλος (Catania) and Μύλος (Monte Saraceno) are also attested on the island). The piece appears to be part of an epitymbion funerary monument, of a type common in Hellenistic Sicily, including along the north coast of the island (e.g. at Cefalu).</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 49.1272 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Manganaro 1999 42 no.22 fig.97 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Plain square letters of regular size without serifs. Mu has vertical first and last, midstrokes descending almost to the line; Alpha appears to have straight bar. Pi has equal length hastae, with overlapping top bar.</p> Line 1-2  50  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
